title: Farstone 2016 Total Backup Recovery Pro v10.10.1(Build 20150918)
description:
Farstone Total Backup Recovery Pro v10.10.1 Build 20150918 Support Windows 10 (7/8/Vista/XP).

Overview

TotalRecovery Pro is an all-in-one system backup and disk imaging software.

FarStone TotalRecovery backs up files & your entire machine, including system files, 
applications, favorites, emails, music, movies, settings, and partitions in a compressed image file. 
What makes TotalRecovery different from other backup software is that it integrates all basic and advanced features 
covering the needs to totally backup & protect your irreplaceable data and computer system.



INSTRUCTIONS Guide:

1. Turn Off Your Antimalware or Antvirus Before using the keygen.
2. Install the program (Do not insert any key when asked during the install!)
3. Run the program and choose "help" menu then "Activate product" menu.
4. You can insert anything for Name & Company. 
5. Open keygen, select "TotalRecoveryV10" product and gnenerate a serial and paste it into program box.
6. In the next screen choose "Other Options" (Important!)
6. Copy your "MAC ID" to the keymaker (right into installation ID section) and click on "Activation"
7. Copy that Activation code into the activation screen and choose "activate now". It's all done!

Note: Every computer has a different MAC ID, it must be copied into "Installation ID" part in the keygen, for
activation code, obviously
